{"tid":2305053,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「印仔開箱」珍煮丹黑糖湯圓","createTime":"2020-11-29T10:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T14:30:51.000Z","uid":33359,"like":97,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"ec00bb70ebf1423b21daac3b940b63b6a4d84e64","tid":2305053,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGZiiyP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGZiiyP.jpg&h=a551b5e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYp6ssa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYp6ssa.jpg&h=34c05c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWPKd7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWPKd7b.jpg&h=e3c69869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢隻湯圓上年已經係台灣出咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過香港好少地方有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日難得見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買包黎試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n湯圓皮唔夠煙UN<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n餡料真係好重黑糖味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重到有少少似藥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋連我呢個螞蟻師都覺得太甜咗D<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5718a84f8d115cb04b83ef07e6b6ef7fe58a14","tid":2305053,"uid":40487,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:15:28.000Z","msg":"開箱師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c45538953b83bedff9eb9d5a2e21958a3c54a7","tid":2305053,"uid":211578,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:15:32.000Z","msg":"湯圓師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hk